__Ways of measuring the number of times "U goes around X"__

* [[Linking number]] $$Lk$$

* [[Twist]] $$Tw$$

The linking number and twist are in general different. However, their difference only depends on $$X$$ (and not in $$U$$). We can therefore define the [[writhing number|Writhe]] as this difference

